p></o:p></span></p>", "sepTemplate": "<p>To access the Electronic Submission Service, please click on the submission-button next to the <strong>type of action</strong> and the <strong>type of model grant agreement</strong> that corresponds to your proposal. You will then be asked to confirm your choice, as it cannot be changed in the submission system. Upon confirmation, you will be linked to the correct entry point.</p>\r\n<p>To access existing draft proposals for this topic, please login to the Funding &amp; Tenders Portal and select the My Proposals page of the My Area section.</p>", "links": [], "additionalDossiers": [], "infoPackDossiers": [], "callDetailsJSONItem": {"latestInfos": [{"approvalDate": "May 11, 2022 1:16:19 PM", "lastChangeDate": "May 11, 2022 1:16:19 PM", "content": "<p><a href=\"https://www.europarl.europa.eu/contracts-and-grants/files/grants/media-and-events/2022/eyy2022/en-faq.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Questions and Answers&nbsp;</a>(Version 10/05/2022)</p>"}, {"approvalDate": "May 4, 2022 12:39:12 PM", "lastChangeDate": "May 4, 2022 12:39:12 PM", "content": "<p><a href=\"https://www.europarl.europa.eu/contracts-and-grants/files/grants/media-and-events/2022/eyy2022/en-faq.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Questions and Answers ( version 04/05/2022)</a></p>"}, {"approvalDate": "Apr 25, 2022 11:17:36 AM", "lastChangeDate": "Apr 25, 2022 11:17:36 AM", "content": "<p><a href=\"https://www.europarl.europa.eu/contracts-and-grants/files/grants/media-and-events/2022/eyy2022/en-faq.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Questions and Answers ( version 22/04/2022)</a></p>"}, {"approvalDate": "Apr 6, 2022 4:09:19 PM", "lastChangeDate": "Apr 6, 2022 4:09:19 PM", "content": "<p><a href=\"https://www.europarl.europa.eu/contracts-and-grants/files/grants/media-and-events/2022/eyy2022/en-faq.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">&nbsp;Questions and Answers ( version 6/04/2022)</a></p>"}, {"approvalDate": "Mar 24, 2022 12:00:00 AM", "lastChangeDate": "Mar 24, 2022 12:00:00 AM", "content": "The submiss